[h]Signal Switch

[i]esoterum-wire-fig2[t]Fig 1.1. A Signal Switch in Action(Placeholder)

The sole existence of the [accent]signal switch[] is to supply circuits with power through user interaction. These components are also commonly used for checking circuits.

[i]esoterum-wire-fig2[t]Fig 1.2. Signal Switch Output(Placeholder)

The signal switch can be toggled by the user at will, outputting to all sides until turned off.

[#4c4c4c]Corporate begs you to not deconstruct signal switches to prevent another 0074-06F2 incident.
